1) cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the use of drones as autonomous systems for surveillance and sensing. 
2) cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of cameras mounted on drones for target coverage. 
3) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes algorithms for optimizing drone usage and coverage. 
4) cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the design and implementation of a complete autonomous surveillance system. 
5) cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the use of drones for surveillance, which could have security implications.
